bt.processor.torrent

Class FilePiecePriorityMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • bt.processor.torrent.FilePiecePriorityMapper

  • public class FilePiecePriorityMapper
extends Object
    A class which creates BitSets of the pieces that are skipped or high priority from the list of files that are prioritized and skipped in a torrent. It also creates a list of all of the files that are not skipped
